WEBVTT

00:01:59.833 --> 00:02:04.601
that your device got a full,
sort of, forensic look over.

00:02:04.625 --> 00:02:07.101
And then I went to lunch.

00:02:07.125 --> 00:02:08.708
(Laughter)

00:02:09.958 --> 00:02:11.643
Ten thousand retweets later,

00:02:11.667 --> 00:02:13.101
(Laughter)

00:02:13.125 --> 00:02:16.542
I had accidentally started a project.

00:02:18.208 --> 00:02:22.518
So every morning,
I woke up and my mailbox was full.

00:02:22.542 --> 00:02:28.351
It was full of the stories
of men and women

00:02:28.375 --> 00:02:33.226
telling me the worst thing
that had ever happened to them.